  "detailed_description": "<u><strong>Spark Vs the Marshmallows</strong></u> is a 4 Player Plug-and-Play co-op/solo adventure where you fights marshmallows, save your fellow flames, and explore a variety of different environments and face off against music based boss battles! Overall this game is a mix of platforming, boss fighting, combat, and exploration! As you progress through each level, you encounter different types of marshmallows and find unique abilities!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Local Multiplayer: Play with up to 4 players locally.</li></ul><strong><u>Fire Swing</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/6bbe4ede9238f98ec967323e83dc27a4.poster.avif?t=1710089547\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/6bbe4ede9238f98ec967323e83dc27a4.webm?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/6bbe4ede9238f98ec967323e83dc27a4.mp4?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/781fb655713984042b5afe1e03b89d38.poster.avif?t=1710089547\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/781fb655713984042b5afe1e03b89d38.webm?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/781fb655713984042b5afe1e03b89d38.mp4?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Unlockable Abilities for Spark the Tiny Flame:</strong></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fire Sling (Melee): A ball of fire that shoots around the player and slings back.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fire Dash (Movement): Burst of fire shoots out of behind the player resulting in boosting forward.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fire Ball (Range): A Fireball shoots out of the player and uses fuel.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Fire Swing</u> (Movement): Grapple onto hooks instantly and swing around gaining velocity to parkour yourself around levels.</li></ul> <br><strong><u>MUSICAL BOSS FIGHTS: (Each with unique attacks, abilities, and weaknesses)</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Marshmallow Dance Battle</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Giant Thumper Marshmallow</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Smore Cannon</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Rocky Road Ice-cream</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/610f4d6cc1b03edecc04e6461889615b.poster.avif?t=1710089547\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/610f4d6cc1b03edecc04e6461889615b.webm?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/610f4d6cc1b03edecc04e6461889615b.mp4?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/206fdf3ccec517f283deabd74a277916.poster.avif?t=1710089547\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/206fdf3ccec517f283deabd74a277916.webm?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088910/extras/206fdf3ccec517f283deabd74a277916.mp4?t=1710089547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vid